music_asset_info.title: Alibi (with Pabllo Vittar & Yseult)

clip.caption_text:
Reality: She’s out here in the Dolomites, struggling for every breath, climbing the steepest trail, looking like she’s about to pass out. Heavy breathing, legs shaking, but still pushing through. 💀😅
Instagram: Majestic shots of her in a gorgeous yellow dress, perfectly posed with the Dolomites, Seceda, and Cadini di Misurina in the background. Pure mountain goddess vibes. ✨🏔️

The struggle behind the scenes is real, but hey, the gram only sees the glam! Share this if you know the difference between hiking reality and Instagram perfection, and follow for more travel laughs and epic views! #HikingStruggles #InstagramVsReality #DolomitesAdventure #SecedaViews #CadiniDiMisurina #TravelHumor #EpicViews
